ed9790fbadfb38e4d660eb1befd87e803d70dec04d936e8cd26def4a9c21240bb7cae8750ae3395aa4761e6738b9e346c86ba57761cfde30efe46d2cb459a7e4  minio.confd
d4295a763fbfd9d86eec74b3a770e1a2a9c4be2e6a13c981cf12586b1c54204ddcb93fb5f05836a1997b0895f3b3ceabba3a88aba979f562bcadad24f702c61d  minio-0.20200501.tar.gz"
